generated_description: passi agro-tech enterprises is a company based in ludhiana, punjab, specializing in the manufacturing of horticultural implements. established in 1969 under the guidance of s. sarbag singh passi, the company produces a range of garden tools including garden rakes, pruning saws, tree pruners, hedge shears, budding knives, khurpa, grass cutting swords, kainchi, and hand hoes. the factory, located in phullanwala, is equipped with modern machinery and technology. the company's products are sold throughout india and internationally, and are recognized and used by various government institutions, agricultural universities, municipal corporations, improvement trusts, departments of horticulture, forestry, and research institutes. passi agro-tech enterprises has received several awards and honors, including the indian society of agricultural engineers' award and the punjab government's horticulture department award for best manufacturer of agricultural implements.
